    "excerpt": "Looking for a job in Dubai? Here are the latest walk-in interviews happening this week across Dubai, Abu Dhabi, and Sharjah. Updated every Monday.",
    "content": "<p><strong>Walk in interview Dubai – UAE today tomorrow (March – April 2026)</strong></p><p>HR Team | Walk In Interview, Career Advice</p><br/><h3>CNS Middle East Walk in Interview in Dubai – March 2026</h3><p>Computer Network Systems (CNS Middle East), a well-known provider of IT and engineering solutions in the Middle East, is organizing a walk-in interview in Dubai for qualified technical professionals. This walk-in drive is aimed at candidates with experience in BIM and CAD disciplines who are looking for opportunities in the UAE job market.</p><br/><div class='article-detail-box'><h4>Walk-In Interview Details</h4><ul><li><strong>Company Name:</strong> Computer Network Systems (CNS Middle East)</li><li><strong>Interview Date:</strong> March 2026</li><li><strong>Interview Time:</strong> 8:30 AM to 5:30 PM</li><li><strong>HR Contact:</strong> Not disclosed</li></ul></div><br/><h3>About the Company</h3><p>CNS Middle East operates in the IT and engineering solutions sector, supporting projects from the planning stage through execution. The company works across infrastructure, commercial, and engineering environments and is involved in delivering technology-driven solutions across the region.</p><br/><h3>Current Job Openings</h3><p><strong>BIM Positions Available:</strong></p><ul><li>Architecture</li><li>Interior Design</li><li>Joinery</li><li>Landscape</li><li>MEP</li><li>Structural</li></ul><p><strong>CAD Positions Available:</strong></p><ul><li>Architecture / Civil</li><li>Joinery / Fit-Out / Interior Design</li><li>Landscape</li><li>MEP</li><li>Rebar / Structural</li></ul><br/><h3>Walk-In Interview Instructions</h3><p>Interested candidates may attend the interview directly on the mentioned date. Applicants are advised to carry:</p><ul><li>Updated CV</li><li>Relevant work documents and portfolio (if applicable)</li></ul><p>Selection and hiring decisions are subject to company requirements and interview performance.</p><br/><h3>Interview Location</h3><p><strong>Venue:</strong> Makeen Building, Airport Road, Garhoud, Dubai<br/><strong>Nearest Metro Station:</strong> GGICO / Garhoud Metro Station</p><br/><div class='article-disclaimer'><p><strong>Disclaimer:</strong> theuaecareer.com is an informational job platform. We are not a recruitment agency and do not charge candidates any fees. Job details are shared for informational purposes only. Candidates are advised to verify interview details directly with the hiring company before attending.</p></div><br/><h3>Nursery Teacher Jobs in Motor City – Walk in Interview</h3><p><strong>Employer:</strong> Emirates British Nursery – Dubai, UAE<br/><strong>Location:</strong> Motor City, Dubai<br/><strong>Curriculum:</strong> Early Years Foundation Stage (British National Curriculum)</p><br/><h3>Job Role:</h3><ul><li>Plan and deliver engaging learning activities.</li><li>Ensure children’s safety, care, and well-being.</li><li>Monitor and record development progress.</li><li>Adapt lessons for the inclusion of all learners.</li><li>Build positive relationships with parents.</li><li>Prepare stimulating classroom displays.</li></ul><br/><h3>Requirements:</h3><ul><li>Degree in Early Childhood/Education OR High School Diploma + CACHE Level 3 Certificate.</li><li>Minimum 2 years’ experience in childcare or early education.</li><li>Strong communication and classroom management skills.</li></ul><br/><h3>Walk in Interview – DHA Pharmacist Jobs in Dubai | GMG Health</h3><p><strong>Company:</strong> GMG – Global Well-being Leader<br/><strong>Location:</strong> Dubai, UAE</p><p>GMG Health is hiring licensed DHA Pharmacists to join our growing pharmacy team in Dubai. You will provide professional pharmaceutical services, dispense prescriptions, and guide customers on the safe and effective use of medications, while ensuring compliance with Dubai Health Authority regulations.</p><br/><h3>Key Requirements:</h3><ul><li>Bachelor’s Degree in Pharmacy</li><li>Valid DHA license (or MOH/DOH convertible to DHA)</li><li>Minimum 1 year of experience as a registered pharmacist</li><li>Strong English & Arabic communication skills</li><li>Flexible to work different shifts and locations</li></ul><br/><h3>Exciting Job Opportunities at Nesto Group – Dubai!</h3><p>Nesto Group is hiring! We’re looking for enthusiastic individuals to join our team at our hypermarket in Deira, Dubai.</p><ul><li><strong>Salesmen / Cashiers:</strong> Age 19–25 years. Customer service focus.</li><li><strong>Pickers / Helpers:</strong> Age 20–30 years. Organized and efficient.</li><li><strong>South Indian / North Indian Cooks:</strong> Age 20–30 years. Culinary experts.</li><li><strong>Shawarma Maker:</strong> Age 20–30 years. Skills to spin out perfect shawarma.</li></ul><br/><h3>Multiple Vacancies: Heavy Bus Drivers – Al Ghazal Transport</h3><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong> Valid UAE Heavy Bus Driving License, 2+ years experience, clean driving record.</p><p><strong>Salary & Benefits:</strong> Attractive salary, overtime, shared accommodation, health insurance, free employment visa.</p><br/><h3>Multiple Vacancies | Dutco Construction LLC (UAE)</h3><p>Dutco Construction LLC is inviting experienced professionals to attend a walk-in interview for multiple roles across commercial, engineering, and management functions.</p><ul><li><strong>Commercial Manager / JS Planning Engineer:</strong> 10-15+ years experience.</li><li><strong>Site Engineer / Quantity Surveyor:</strong> 5-12 years experience.</li><li><strong>AutoCAD Draftsman / Document Controller:</strong> 5-8 years experience.</li></ul><br/><div class='article-detail-box'><h4>Dutco Walk-In Details</h4><ul><li><strong>Interview Date:</strong> Saturday, 24 February 2026</li><li><strong>Interview Time:</strong> 09:00 AM – 02:00 PM</li><li><strong>Location:</strong> DBB Contracting LLC Dutco Complex, Jabal Ali, Dubai</li></ul></div>",
